            "id": 6010169,
            "title": "川馬開撕AI股中槍倒地 三大法人賣超123.24億元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股今 (6) 日在台積電、AI 股熄火，以及迎來周末下，呈現量縮震盪，終場小跌 13.77 點收 21660.66 點，成交金額 2942 億元；三大法人合計賣超 123.24 億元。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010169%2Fl%2F0f0f1a2d3f9a23da5589e1011746df6f.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010169%2Fl%2F0f0f1a2d3f9a23da5589e1011746df6f.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010169%2Fl%2F0f0f1a2d3f9a23da5589e1011746df6f.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010169%2Fl%2F0f0f1a2d3f9a23da5589e1011746df6f.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010169%2Fl%2F0f0f1a2d3f9a23da5589e1011746df6f.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010169%2Fl%2F0f0f1a2d3f9a23da5589e1011746df6f.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010169%2Fl%2F0f0f1a2d3f9a23da5589e1011746df6f.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010169%2Fl%2F0f0f1a2d3f9a23da5589e1011746df6f.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010169%2Fl%2F0f0f1a2d3f9a23da5589e1011746df6f.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010169%2Fl%2F0f0f1a2d3f9a23da5589e1011746df6f.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010169%2Fl%2F0f0f1a2d3f9a23da5589e1011746df6f.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010169%2Fl%2F0f0f1a2d3f9a23da5589e1011746df6f.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010169%2Fl%2F0f0f1a2d3f9a23da5589e1011746df6f.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010169%2Fl%2F0f0f1a2d3f9a23da5589e1011746df6f.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010169%2Fl%2F0f0f1a2d3f9a23da5589e1011746df6f.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010169%2Fl%2F0f0f1a2d3f9a23da5589e1011746df6f.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010169%2Fl%2F0f0f1a2d3f9a23da5589e1011746df6f.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">川馬開撕AI股中槍倒地 三大法人賣超123.24億元。(圖:shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>觀察三大法人今天籌碼動向，外資賣超 136.73 億元；自營商賣超 24.55 億元；投信買超 38.04 億元；三大法人合計賣超 123.24 億元</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--></main>",
